    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s been meticulously maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
