      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, featuring a deep, mirror-like gloss with absolutely zero stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive paper trail to prove it. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. Every button, switch, and feature operates with the crispness of a brand-new machine. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection and refuses to settle for anything less than a flawless example, this vehicle stands in a league of its own.",
